Layered Armor															CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat																																					PREMULT:1,[PREPROFWITHARMOR:1,TYPE.Light],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Armor Proficiency (Light)]	PREMULT:1,[PREPROFWITHARMOR:1,TYPE.Medium],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Armor Proficiency (Medium)]	PREMULT:1,[PREPROFWITHARMOR:1,TYPE.Heavy],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Armor Proficiency (Heavy)]										PRESTAT:1,CON=15					PREVARGTEQ:ArmorTrainingLVL,2													DESC:Wear light armor under your heavy armor.																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.64											BENEFIT:You may wear both a set of light magic armor and heavy magic armor simultaneously. Your armor bonus is equal to the heavy armor's armor bonus +1. You gain no benefit from the light armor's enhancement bonus. Your armor check penalty is equal to the worse of the two penalties - 1. Your maximum Dexterity bonus to AC is equal to the worse of the two bonuses - 1 (minimum 0). You are considered to be wearing a suit of heavy armor even if the heavy armor would normally count as medium armor. You gain the benefits of all the magic abilities granted by the heavy armor. You may also gain one selected magic ability granted by the light armor (except the enhancement bonus, or any version of slick or shadow). As a standard action, you may change which of the light armor's magic abilities you have selected.
