Reflect Spells															CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat				PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Ki Pool	PREABILITY:4,CATEGORY=FEAT,Deflect Arrows,Deflect Spells,Improved Unarmed Strike,Snatch Arrow																																																																						PRESTAT:2,DEX=17,WIS=17																					DESC:Redirect a spell at another target.																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.67											BENEFIT:When you successfully deflect a spell or ability using the Deflect Spell feat, you may choose to immediately spend a 2nd point from your ki pool as a swift action to redirect the spell or ability to a new target. The spell or ability's maximum range must be long enough to go from the original attacker, to you, to the new target, or the spell fails to reach. You make any required attack roll to hit the new target, but all other effects are determined by the original caster.
