Extra Spells Known							CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General.Magister										PRECLASS:1,SPELLCASTER=3																						PRESPELLCAST:MEMORIZE=N																PRETEXT:Spontaneous spellcasting class level 3	DESC:Gain two additional spells known.										STACK:YES	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NOCHOICE												BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Extra Spells Known|1										SOURCEPAGE:p.60	BENEFIT:You gain two additional spells known for one spontaneous spellcasting class you have levels in. You may never use this feat to know more spells at any level than you know at each level below it.
