Spell Finesse								CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General																																																																DESC:Change your spellcasting ability.																												BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Spell Finesse Stat|1										SOURCEPAGE:p.70	BENEFIT:All your spellcasting calculations are based off a selected mental attribute, including the maximum level of spell you can cast, spell save DCs, and bonus spells/day. If you have spellcasting abilities from multiple sources, you can change all of them to this same attribute. Once this feat is taken and your new spellcasting attribute is selected, it cannot be changed.
